SPELL NAME  : High Mitra tell           | Emote High Mitra tell
SPELL SYNTAX: Htell <message>           | Ehtell <emoted message>
SPELL COST  : NONE                      | NONE
DESCRIPTION : This ability sends out the <message> to all on-line High
	      level Clerics and Paladins. These are the guild level 15 
              clerics and paladins.
